            Founded in 1967, Balchem Corporation offers its line of products, which includes packaged specialty chemicals for use in health care, choline chloride and microencapsulation technologies, for a range of industries throughout the world. The company consists primarily of three business segments: encapsulated/nutritional products, ARC Specialty Products and BCP Ingredients. Balchem employs more than 200 people throughout the United States who are engaged in the diverse activities of developing its company into a market leader. Balchem Corporation s headquarters are located in New Hampton, N.Y. Its manufacturing facilities are located in Slate Hill, N.Y.; Green Pond, S.C.; Verona, Mo.; and Channahon, Ill.
          






















