Real People, Real Science, Real Results
 


 
 







For more than 40 years, Balchem has perfected the art of protecting nutrient quality and viability and, over the past decade, has delivered the highest quality nutrients on the market. With Balchem on your team, you can rest assured that we’ll provide the people, science, and results you need to reach your goals.
Balchem provides state-of-the-art solutions and the finest quality products for a range of industries worldwide, including human nutrition, animal nutrition, and industrial applications. With more than 300 employees globally, we have experienced, knowledgeable people to address your unique situations and offer candid responses to your nutrition questions.
We apply proven science and industry-leading technologies backed by years of success in the feed industry. You will not find a more experienced and committed team of scientists and researchers strategically aligned to identify and develop high-quality, innovative, proprietary products designed to meet your animal nutrition, productivity and wellness needs.
But in the end, it all comes down to results — real results you can count on, results that help you meet your goals.
That’s our passion. That’s our promise. That’s what you get with Balchem
 
